ike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:58:27.000Z","msg":"當年Band 5尾畢業。<br />\n而家Hku master. <br />\n<br />\n果時心態是，要一直讀書你先可以明正言順咁去玩所以就符符碌碌咁讀落去。"},{"pid":"e7472f70538563b95b9bada33baef2db7d603407","tid":6300,"uid":40881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學校勁遲放study leave 如何自救？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nstudy leave真係唔會有咩起死回生 除左oral科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而係mock考完 對返上年data 估你係咩grade基本上就係咩grade  唔會差得好遠 所以加油溫mock報mock啦<br />\n利申 已上岸"},{"pid":"1995cf98b3fa72b8b0dcb48c01ce011e2eda1dad","tid":6300,"uid":27260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學校勁遲放study leave 如何自救？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nstudy leave真係唔會有咩起死回生 除左oral科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而係mock考完 對返上年data 估你係咩grade基本上就係咩grade  唔會差得好遠 所以加油溫mock報mock啦<br />\n利申 已上岸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n利伸mock 懶得温 老師預history u 中史1 study leave 攻西史 棄中史 點撚知兩個都有4 中史俾阿sir 貼中兩題 淨係背辛亥革命同唐朝 天主教 我入試場感動到仆街"},{"pid":"d866eaa6dd93fdfa15f02f0622dadd8b049d294d","tid":6300,"uid":10951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:47:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學校勁遲放study leave 如何自救？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你宜家有無話點樣溫緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4093da04ccde2e9ac685762aefccbc0af57f58c8","tid":6300,"uid":10951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:54:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求救今年中五，目標3322，英文好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中五有心追唔怕遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我大約都係呢個時候識諗 <br />\n有無興趣試下睇書？<br />\n 我起初都係英文坐1望2左右<br />\n果陣呀sir叫去借d英文書for English learner(例如企鵝出版社） <br />\n我由medium level睇起<br />\n過程我淨係要求自己睇得明 無話點背到生字 <br />\n去到中六呀sir都話我進步左唔少<br />\n<br />\n咁你其他科呢？選修科？"},{"pid":"d7f881da7fc31d3f33ebe0fe1bd6d95fb4c275ad","tid":6300,"uid":10951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:56:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Band3<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係驚語文科<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，其他都操到七七八八</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a465f693262fcfa68396f053d6eb677bb9c4b3","tid":6300,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:06:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75b7abd43ce052d1837c231edcb20eddbae9697a","tid":6300,"uid":10951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學校勁遲放study leave 如何自救？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你宜家有無話點樣溫緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n操pp 加睇補習notes</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔洗咁擔心study leave <br />\n只要有平時善用時間真係分別不大<br />\n<br />\n果陣我間學校都係咁濕尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要留住d學生驚死佢地唔溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我會放學係自修室留到好夜先走 <br />\n同埋一上廢既堂就做自己野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁你既目標係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf332a9fa3181cc667afac5185e945f7c386fde7","tid":6300,"uid":10586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:06:21.000Z","msg":"算係band3中top果批人<br />\n但成日好怕maths同eng <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" clas