 class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMaths有無操下卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英文就真係要睇你有無心去浸下 不過可以由少少開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英文我有兩個好勁嘅補習同時跟緊應該一定有3-4<br />\nmaths有2-3但好想有5</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMaths你可以試下一步步操 <br />\n以前我呀sir教既方法我覺得你可以參考下<br />\n先操part A(1)先 操到好熟都無咩錯 <br />\n咁就起碼level 2/3 <br />\n之後就A2 最後就B <br />\n如此類推 咁就可以提高效率同埋按番自己既程度操 <br />\n<br />\n至於MC有時候除左講你係咪真係識之外 <br />\n亦都好睇你熟唔熟佢果d方法 <br />\n所以做完記住果d你覺得唔熟又或者做得好慢既題目<br />\n睇下題解有無用d特別方法去做 試下自己跟住做<br />\n做到自己識<br />\n<br />\n當年小弟part B都拎唔係好多分 最後都5*到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35a3b882608275ffbe5d06a6652c57a9ba5f059","tid":6300,"uid":10951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學校勁遲放study leave 如何自救？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你宜家有無話點樣溫緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n操pp 加睇補習notes</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔洗咁擔心study leave <br />\n只要有平時善用時間真係分別不大<br />\n<br />\n果陣我間學校都係咁濕尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要留住d學生驚死佢地唔溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我會放學係自修室留到好夜先走 <br />\n同埋一上廢既堂就做自己野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁你既目標係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n18,9分左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無覺得好大壓力呀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e96fcd32fddf90284b975f7d38af839cb62123","tid":6300,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:56:43.000Z","msg":"一齊ive見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 band3尾過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdfec1dc0a4bee49a70e8551a9ce8d9eefba99ad","tid":6300,"uid":14721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:33:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>算係band3中top果批人<br />\n但成日好怕maths同eng <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMaths有無操下卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英文就真係要睇你有無心去浸下 不過可以由少少開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英文我有兩個好勁嘅補習同時跟緊應該一定有3-4<br />\nmaths有2-3但好想有5</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n數學卷應該做多d pp<br />\n同埋要計下點樣先可以拎到 level 5 <br />\n你要知道拎5唔一定要全部野識晒<br />\n重點温書都好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 畀心機"},{"pid":"743706648955936ef0ff1540a66c9b1816b584be","tid":6300,"uid":43604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:08:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學校勁遲放study leave 如何自救？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己請假啦 我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75a15002143ab070b3be30d15c34c6425179d60","tid":6300,"uid":10586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:36:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>算係band3中top果批人<br />\n但成日好怕maths同eng <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMaths有無操下卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英文就真係要睇你有無心去浸下 不過可以由少少開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英文我有兩個好勁嘅補習同時跟緊應該一定有3-4<br />\nmaths有2-3但好想有5</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n數學卷應該做多d pp<br />\n同埋要計下點樣先可以拎到 level 5 <br />\n你要知道拎5唔一定要全部野識晒<br />\n重點温書都好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 畀心機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家有種沉迷左Past paper心態<br />\n個心成日好想快啲放學返屋企做數做paper<br />\n究竟呢個心態係好事定壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次呀sir 比左本2012 sp pp -2016 pp PartA(1)<br />\n叫我地返屋企慢慢做<br />\n點知我果日放學即刻衝返屋企做<br />\n由7點做到10點飯都無食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f477179fbfdf98cfe29c1af35f466320635c013","tid":6300,"uid":10586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>算係band3中top果批人<br />\n但成日好怕maths同eng <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMaths有無操下卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英文就真係要睇你有無心去浸下 不過可以由少少開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英文我有兩個好勁嘅補習同時跟緊應該一定有3-4<br />\nmaths有2-3但好想有5</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMaths你可以試下一步步操 <br />\n以前我呀sir教既方法我覺得你可以參考下<br />\n先操part A(1)先 操到好熟都無咩錯 <br />\n咁就起碼level 2/3 <br />\n之後就A2 最後就B <br />\n如此類推 咁就可以提高效率同埋按番自己既程度操 <br />\n<br />\n至於MC有時候除左講你係咪真係識之外 <br />\n亦都好睇你熟唔熟佢果d方法 <br />\n所以做完記住果d你覺得唔熟又或者做得好慢既題目<br />\n睇下題解有無用d特別方法去做 試下自己跟住做<br />\n做到自己識<br />\n<br />\n當年小弟part B都拎唔係好多分 最後都5*到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nA1 岩98%到啦(prove 題reason唔多記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n但得4個月夠唔夠由3上5？"},{"pid":"15d199e5a419f86f88d73be58f22e514bb584946","tid":6300,"uid":10951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:31:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>算係band3中top果批人<br />\n但成日好怕maths同eng <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMaths有無操下卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英文就真係要睇你有無心去浸下 不過可以由少少開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英文我有兩個好勁嘅補習同時跟緊應該一定有3-4<br />\nmaths有2-3但好想有5</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMaths你可以試下一步步操 <br />\n以前我呀sir教既方法我覺得你可以參考下<br />\n先操part A(1)先 操到好熟都無咩錯 <br />\n咁就起碼level 2/3 <br />\n之後就A2 最後就B <br />\n如此類推 咁就可以提高效率同埋按番自己既程度操 <br />\n<br />\n至於MC有時候除左講你係咪真係識之外 <br />\n亦都好睇你熟唔熟佢果d方法 <br />\n所以做完記住果d你覺得唔熟又或者做得好慢既題目<br />\n睇下題解有無用d特別方法去做 試下自己跟住做<br />\n做到自己識<br />\n<br />\n當年小弟part B都拎唔係好多分 最後都5*到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nA1 岩98%到啦(prove 題reason唔多記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n但得4個月夠唔夠由3上5？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未必唔得 不過唔試就一定唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記住每一份野唔係做完就算 我自己要完全明白哂自己點解錯 確定自己識做 同埋用最快既方法做先叫做完一份<br />\n我果陣身邊好多人淨係追求個量 結果忽略左最重要既一環"},{"pid":"3adeff520d6134c8eb840811b220b5d4e2a65f5c","tid":6300,"uid":48670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:16:50.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n如果你冇咩時間剩<br />\n真係唔好搶攻語文科<br />\n語文科真係要時間浸同埋要少少天份<br />\n保住唔斷腳就ok了<br />\n除非你大學揀個科有特別要求就另講<br />\n<br />\n不如將啲時間放落maths或者elective<br />\n可能效果更高"},{"pid":"5a1774f9a08755e1692490dbca0b4efb36f98064","tid":6300,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:28:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}